Documentation for libtricubic can be found in doc/. Extended documentation is available at http://gyre.cds.caltech.edu/pub/software/tricubic/doc/

Installation instruction are in file INSTALL. However, the following procedure should work for you

%gunzip tricubic-1.0.tar.gz
%tar -xvf tricubic-1.0.tar
%cd tricubic-1.0/
%./configure
%make

To install for all users (need root password):
%su
%make install

To install for a single user
%./configure --prefix=/home/userlogin
%make
%make install


